values:
well i got my cell phone today that shit is tiiiiiiiiight. i guess. but yea its late and there is nothing to do so i decided to update my journal. maybe i'll find something to do later on....just maybe haha yea right. i talked to bety today that was also tiiiiiiiiiiight. it's been a chill day except that i had to wake up at 4!!!!! in the morning and that shit isn't tiiiiiiiiight. i can't sleep i woke up way too late. i don't know what to say and i bet someone's smart ass is gonna reply to this entry and say your dumb or something of that nature. but that's cool cause.........yeah i dont know lol. alright peace out people. live life. chill -ig








bety is my lady

everytime i wake up i have a nasty headache. i haven't been doing anything lately but it hurts...is it that i sleep for over 12 hours? or man someone tell me what it is! i was home early for the first time last night in the longest.....8:47! beat that baby! and i'm banned from my friends house for 1 week, or something like that but i don't think im going to go there anymore. but who knows we'll see. and if i don't go it's not because i don't like anyone it's just cause i guess. maybe casue i know i could do something productive instead of just hanging around. i need $$$ anyway. and i gotta start practicing more often...music - guitar and drums. and this ones to erick....don't fall off your roof man u'll find a way up there! lol
 -ig




sweet i'm missing you

so i've finally decided what i want to be......shit a fucking stuntman. then when i get hurt im gonna be laying there staring at the sun helpless, regreting why i was this to begin with, fuck i dunno but im gonna be a stuntman. alright but i almost died twice today, and you gotta bail me out. if you do i'll give u 5 bucks and everything....ok ok im done......but maybe today will be my day. peace -ig
i feel a bit of sorrow but at the same time i know its all gonna be ok. see you soon =/ -ig

...i justwoke up and i'm tired. listening to music wondering what this day has in store for me...(knock on wood) yesterday was i'd say a bi-polar day or something like that. real low points cause of some drama and high points cause i kicked it with my homies. august 21 im gonna see my 48 buddies. so thats gonna be a lot of fun i haven't hung out with those guys in ages. we're all gonna go back to last summer and kick it and do everything we used to do. last night was cold...i started freezing when i got home. or maybe it should be that way winter seems to be my season anyway. people seem to be a lot cooler with each other, no drama none of that shit. well pace. i'm out. -ig

p.s. -----scattered......torn up and ripped apart
...not much to say. just glad im alive and this summer has been by the far one of th best i've had. thank you to all the people that have made it fun. you know who you are. =) sweet n' juicy.   -ig

... so just turn off the lights. do what you want to do. 

sup. last night was actually bad ass just kickin it there with my homie we had tacos at 10 and from there we stayed up til 5:30 in the morning. and now it's whatever time it is and i feel tired as shmuck. but whatever. life's good summer is almost over which is really cheap. i wish summers could be longer cause once a summer gets going and good...it's gone. i talked to bety =) about a few things and they went pretty well. got it all cleared up. i dont know what else to say except that...damn BEEiNg alive right now is bad ass...not that i ever want to be dead or anything but damn it's cool!!!! haha alright peoples take care -nacho

From throat and eyes came winter and reasons. I'm told to carry on. Sad overwhelms my senses drown. oh I feel dependent The feeling that you weren't honest before I can't shake it. Make the same mistake twice, Flash of red and green all over me. Freeze the things that you love. Ash from what had formed all over. We count the days left, 21 And all I know Honestly, could I be protected With you suddenly gone? The feeling that you're really gone I can't shake it...   


p.s. that sucks             -ig

so my boss got mad at tony and i cause we didn't go to the boxing gym. we explained to him that the trainer got mad cause we didn't have our equipment...yet again. but anywho i had fun yesterday i was so bored that i pretty much drank all day, didn't get drunk cause i would only end up falling asleep wherever i was at. i've come to realize that my friends and i aren't the same anymore, or maybe we never were to begin with. they don't make any plans, they don't like hanging out with different people, some are picky, some are submissive, i guess it's just a power struggle. but eh whatever. i don't get it. =\ or maybe these are my friends for the rest of my life. i just don't understand. i've met a few different people during these past few weeks and they are kewl peoples! unfortunately one of them is going back to school soon which really blows. well see ya -ig

last night was a drag, i was at gage bowl hanging out with some kewl peoples. yea it was the usual but at the same time it was different i was sore, from my workout at the boxing gym, and i wasn't wasted...i kinda shocked myself when i wasn't. and i think i need to stop smoking, my partner in crime/bestfriend/enemy handed me a pamphlet that read "HOW TO STOP SMOKING FOR A DAY" a day i've done that so many times...but thanks to SOMEONE *coughbetycough* i'm back into it...im j/k =) but anywho yea my friends decided they wanted to go to the races and i was going to stay but i had no ride home well i did but i didn't wanna wait for an hour doing nothing at gage bowl. so i went with them and there were NO RACES!!!!! what a waste a time and to top that off i was the one who had to go to the liquor store and get them their beer...what a bunch of bitches! haha well yesterday was a bad ass day and today...well lets see how that goes....hey bety, wendy, or jess....i lost your #'s =( maybe i'll asksome for them. sorry k peace out and o yea here's a cool quote that i found...it kinda made me think about how i shouldn't forget the past...the least i could do is acknowledge it...and i'll end it with this quote. see ya =) -ig

     ---those who do not remember the past are condemned to repeat it,----- some famous guy from the book The Social Animal---
